%% useCare — wireframe & navigation flow
%% Source of truth: docs/useCare.excalidraw (the sketch)
%% This file mirrors the sketch as a Mermaid flowchart so it is diffable,
%% renderable in GitHub/Notion/VSCode, and readable by humans and LLMs.

flowchart TD
    Login["🔐 Login / Register
    -----------------
    • email
    • password
    • [Login] [Register]"]

    Login -->|role = ADMIN| AdminHome
    Login -->|role = DOCTOR| DoctorCalendar
    Login -->|role = PATIENT| PatientHome

    %% =============================================================
    subgraph ADMIN["👑 ADMIN"]
        direction TB

        AdminHome["Admin Dashboard
        -----------------
        Side menu:
          • user CRUD (approval also)
          • specialties
          • Appointments
          • System settings"]

        AdminUsers["Users List  [X close]
        -----------------
        | Name | Role | ? |
        | Name | Role | ? |
        | ...                |
        (? = pending-approval badge)"]

        AdminApprove["Approve User
        -----------------
        Name:  ____________
        Role:  ____________
        Desc:  ____________
        [ Approve ]   [ X ]"]

        AdminSpecialties["Specialties
        -----------------
        list + add / edit / delete"]

        AdminAppointments["Appointments
        -----------------
        global table of all appointments"]

        AdminSettings["System Settings"]

        AdminHome --> AdminUsers
        AdminUsers -->|click pending ?| AdminApprove
        AdminHome --> AdminSpecialties
        AdminHome --> AdminAppointments
        AdminHome --> AdminSettings
    end

    %% =============================================================
    subgraph DOCTOR["🩺 DOCTOR"]
        direction TB

        DoctorCalendar["Doctor Calendar  (month view)
        -----------------
        MUI DateCalendar + dynamic-data
        https://mui.com/x/react-date-pickers/date-calendar/#dynamic-data

        Each day cell shows:
          # of appointments that day
          (replaces the ⏱︎ icon — see sketch note)
        [ + ] on a day = set day as available"]

        DoctorConfirmAvailable{{"Confirm
        -----------------
        'Set as available for appointments?'
        [ Confirm ]   [ Cancel ]"}}

        DoctorDaySchedule["Day Schedule  (00H → 24H)
        -----------------
        Hour grid with patient slots:
          ⏱︎ 16:30  patient: samir
          ⏱︎ 17:00  patient: …
        Click a slot → appointment detail"]

        DoctorAppointment["Appointment Detail (doctor view)
        -----------------
        2026/26/65    16:30 PM
        status  ▼   (dropdown)
        patient info
        doctor info
        Appointment info
        Doctor's Notes: __________
        [ Save ]"]

        DoctorCalendar -->|click + on a day| DoctorConfirmAvailable
        DoctorConfirmAvailable -->|confirm| DoctorDaySchedule
        DoctorCalendar -->|click a day| DoctorDaySchedule
        DoctorDaySchedule -->|click slot| DoctorAppointment
    end

    %% =============================================================
    subgraph PATIENT["🧑 PATIENT"]
        direction TB

        PatientHome["Patient Home
        -----------------
        'Select Doctor from the table below'
        | Doctor | Specialty | ? |
        | samir  | …         | ? |
        | samir  | …         | ? |"]

        PatientWeek["Week Picker
        -----------------
        MUI WeekPicker
        https://mui.com/x/react-date-pickers/date-calendar/#week-picker
        pick a week → see availability"]

        PatientAvailable["Available Appointments
        -----------------
        ⏱︎ 2026/26/65  16:30 PM  Doctor
        ⏱︎ 2026/26/65  16:30 PM  Doctor
        ⏱︎ 2026/26/65  16:30 PM  Doctor
        click slot → book"]

        PatientMyAppointments["My Appointments
        -----------------
        | date | time | status | edit/delete |
        | …    | …    | …      | edit/delete |
        | …    | …    | …      | edit/delete |"]

        PatientHome -->|pick doctor| PatientWeek
        PatientWeek --> PatientAvailable
        PatientAvailable -->|book| PatientMyAppointments
        PatientHome --> PatientMyAppointments
    end

    %% =============================================================
    %% Cross-role notes pulled from the sketch:
    %% • All 3 roles share the same nav stubs in the sketch
    %%   (user CRUD / specialties / appointments / system settings)
    %%   — but in practice only ADMIN exercises all four.
    %% • '?' badges in tables = pending-approval / status indicator.
    %% • The clock icon ⏱︎ in day cells is replaced by the
    %%   appointment count (sketch annotation).
